            </ul>
            <br />

            <h2>2. Eligibility for Replacement</h2>
            <p>Replacement will be provided under the following conditions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Damaged Items:</strong> If the item is delivered in damaged condition, such as torn
                    packaging, leaks, or spills.</li>
                <li><strong>Expired Products:</strong> If the product delivered has already passed its expiration date.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Incorrect Delivery:</strong> If the wrong item or quantity has been delivered.</li>
                <li><strong>Defective Items:</strong> If the product is defective or not usable (e.g., spoiled fruits,
                    vegetables, or non-functional packaged goods).</li>
                <li><strong>Missing Items:</strong> If items listed in the order are missing from the delivery.</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h2>3. Non-Eligible Items</h2>
            <p>The following items are not eligible for replacement:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Items that are not marked as "Replacement Available" during purchase.</li>
                <li><strong>Change of Mind:</strong> Requests for replacements due to personal preferences or
                    dissatisfaction with the taste, appearance, or size of the product.</li>
                <li>Items that have been partially used or consumed by the customer.</li>
                <li>Products showing signs of tampering or improper storage after delivery.</li>
                <li>Orders placed under clearance sale or with a “No Replacement” tag.</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h2>4. Process for Replacement</h2>
            <h3>Initiate the Request:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Contact customer support via [Provide Contact Information: App/Email/Phone] within 24 hours of
                    delivery.</li>
                <li>Share details like order number and images/videos of the product highlighting the issue.</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h3>Inspection and Approval:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Our team will verify the issue based on the shared proof and may arrange a pick-up for further
                    inspection.</li>
                <li>For perishable items, immediate approval may be granted based on evidence provided.</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h3>Replacement Delivery:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Once approved, the replacement item will be delivered within [Specify timeframe: 12-24 hours],
