            </ul>
            <br />

            <h2>5. Refund in Case of Unavailability</h2>
            <p>If the replacement product is unavailable, we will offer:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Full Refund to your original payment method.</li>
                <li>Store Credit or a coupon for future purchases, as per your choice.</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h2>6. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensure the items remain unused and are stored appropriately until the replacement process is
